Lightweight MonteCarlo simulator written in the lords language c.

Install instructions gnu/linux
Prerequisites musl/glibc, busybox/standard gnu utils, gnu make, gcc.
Commands:
make install

Install instructions windows (not recommended)
Prerequisites hyprv
Commands:
wsl --install debian
wsl 
sudo apt install ncurses-dev build-essentials gcc git
make install

To disable ncurses support disable the use flag.
